## Breakpoint System

### Tailwind Default Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Min Width | Target Devices |
|------------|-----------|----------------|
| `sm` | 640px | Large phones (landscape) |
| `md` | 768px | Tablets |
| `lg` | 1024px | Laptops |
| `xl` | 1280px | Desktops |
| `2xl` | 1536px | Large screens |

